  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">About Insight Hunter</p>
    <p>Insight Hunter is a leading provider of financial intelligence tools designed to empower founders, teams, and enterprises with actionable insights. Founded in 2025, our mission is to simplify finance through AI-powered solutions, eliminating the need for spreadsheets and disconnected tools.</p>
    <p>Our company is based in Atlanta, with a team of experts in AI, finance, and software development. We focus on innovation, privacy, and user-centric design. Key milestones include the launch of our Lite edition for solo users and the expansion to enterprise-grade features in Full.</p>
    <p>For technical details, visit our tech page. Stay updated with company news and announcements on the updates and news sections. If you have questions, explore our FAQs or reach out via the contact page.</p>
  </section>
